"JD Edward" Senior Specialist
Confidential Company - ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/05 13:35:32
Ref. JB3016312
Job Description
Job Scope
Maintain and support existing applications on JDE; handle users’ requests.
Main Duties and Responsibilities:
Assist in the implementation of
JDE
Perform daily and monthly operations tasks to ensure smooth work flow
Create and modify JDE reports and applications to satisfy business needs based on demand;
Generate and update JDE technical and business documentations in order to facilitate work on JDE software;
Perform technical maintenance on JDE: packages, menus, users security, etc;
Assist in the monthly and yearly closing to ensure smooth running operation;
Support users on JDE in order to resolve daily issues;
Perform other job related duties as assigned.
Skills
Education
Bachelor’s degree in Business Computer/Computer Science, or equivalent
Experience
At least 2 to 3 years’ relevant experience
